00:00:00.570 --> 00:00:03.960
There is one more property you can set. You can disable users

00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:06.990
zooming entirely by setting user scalable

00:00:06.990 --> 00:00:10.350
to no. Fundamentally, you really shouldn't do

00:00:10.350 --> 00:00:14.330
this. It's bad for accessibility and you're more likely to just annoy your

00:00:14.330 --> 00:00:18.070
users by preventing them from zooming than to make their experience any better.

